OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FThis morning will be cloudy
OL,6,Fwith spells of rain, occasionally
OL,7,Fheavy. Rain will turn more showery
OL,8,Fthis afternoon, some brightness
OL,9,Fpossible along the east coast.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FThis evening will see a few
OL,12,Fshowers. The rest of the night will
OL,13,Fsee variable amounts of cloud with
OL,14,Ffurther showers or longer spells of
OL,15,Frain.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSaturday:FAny overnight showers soon
OL,18,Fdying out. Then the rest of the day
OL,19,Fwill be dry with sunny spells.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
